Package: astros-core
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, systemd
Maintainer: AstrOS Team <aiastros2025@gmail.com>
Description: AstrOS AI Agent - Your Intelligent Desktop Assistant
 AstrOS is an intelligent AI assistant that integrates seamlessly with
 your Ubuntu desktop. It provides natural language interaction powered
 by MistralAI's Ministral-8B model.
 .
 Features:
  - Natural language conversation
  - System-wide integration
  - Auto-start on boot
  - Secure API key management
  - Low resource usage (< 50MB RAM)
  - Fast response times (< 2s)
 .
 This package includes:
  - AI agent daemon
  - Systemd service configuration
  - Command-line interface
  - First-boot setup wizard
Homepage: https://github.com/CoreOrganizations/AstrOS
